Package parsing.syntaxTree.expressions

Interface Expression

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Aggregation, ArgDeclaration, ArgList, Association, AttributeList, ClassContent, ClassDeclaration, DataItem, Declaration, DeclarationList, Generalization, Identifier, Model, Multiplicity, Operation, OperationList, Role, Roles, SubClassNames, SyntaxTree, TwoRole, Type

    public interface Expression
    General representation of an Expression of the BNF grammar.

    Every grammar rule of the BNF syntax must be declared as a class and must implement this interface.
